Static Function GeraSC7Tmp(xSC7,xSF4,xSB1)
Local cAliTMPSC7
Local aFieldSC7
Local aTmpFields
Local nX
Local cSX3Campo
Local aStruField
Local oTempSC7
Local cSC7Table
Local cQuery
Local cQryFields
Local cQrySelect

	cAliTMPSC7 := CriaTrab(NIL,.F.)

